<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="S" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Slug" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Slug,</orth> a kind of snail; used as the symbol of slowness and laziness: <cit><quote>thou drone, thou snail, thou s.</quote> <bibl n="shak. err 2.2.196" default="NO" valid="yes">Err. II, 2, 196</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>what a s. is Hastings,</quote> <bibl n="shak. r3 3.1.22" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 III, 1, 22</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>fie, you s. a-bed,</quote> <bibl n="shak. rom 4.5.2" default="NO" valid="yes">Rom. IV, 5, 2</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>